title: Serene apartment homes in Oak Hill
posting_body: ['Text ID # 9119A to my cell for more info!', 'SERENE APARTMENTS IN OAK HILL AUSTIN TX', 'Spacious Floor Plans.', 'Choose between our one-, two- and three-bedroom apartments, each designed with layouts perfect for individuals or families of all sizes.', 'The open-concept design of our floor plans means your living & storage spaces are optimized to ensure you feel right at home.', 'Photo Gallery.', 'Browse our photo gallery to see exactly what sets Hills apart from the rest.', 'Between our resort-style pool, well-kept grounds and thoughtfully designed floor plans, you’ll see why Hills is more than just a home.', 'Convenient Amenities.', 'From our on-site laundry facility, to our swimming pool and movie rental service, we have all the amenities you need to both relax and get your day-to-day tasks done.', 'Relaxing Location.', 'Located mere minutes from downtown, but also tucked away in the prestigious neighborhood of Oak Hill, Hills places you in the best of both worlds.', 'Take advantage of some of the finest schools, parks and community features Austin has to offer.']
